{"tid":337024,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"我動物台護花使者瀧三將會改名做Leafa","createTime":"2017-07-27T02:51:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-27T19:55:18.000Z","uid":57911,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"200cc4daa6645c99d43aa0bbdec88f4861da3c75","tid":337024,"uid":57911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T02:51:11.000Z","msg":"為咗方便繼續狙擊牙直<br />\n我動物台護花使者瀧三將會短暫改名做Leafa<br />\n直到牙直正式收皮為止<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nbonus<br />\n<a href=\"http://i.imgur.com/xhPPVd2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FxhPPVd2.jpg&d=JLAdynOSApH72bnt5W8YUJZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=0dfbf140\" target=\"_blank\">http://i.imgur.com/xhPPVd2.jpg</a><br />\n有會然話鬥丁得多直葉<br />\n會然瀧三展示出3本直葉咸濕書籍"},{"pid":"fdafbf2ce17bd58986859aefd3f1120531d595a6","tid":337024,"uid":57911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T02:55:55.000Z","msg":"身上掛住桐谷直葉名牌嘅牙直一上線，所有人便都看着他笑，有的叫道：「牙直，桐谷直葉又出咗新figure！」他不回答，留言說：「我動物台小直&hellip;」便排出三四個post。他們又故意的高聲嚷道：「你咁中意直葉一定都會買啦！」牙直睜大眼晴說：「中意都唔一定要買&hellip;」「中意唔一定要買？早幾日另外一個post見到你買咗雷姆公仔，掛住桐谷直葉個名牌仲搵咁多藉口，知唔知醜。」牙直便漲紅了臉，額上的青筋條條綻出，爭辯道：「冇俾錢買都可以好中意！&hellip;&hellip;中唔中意，點可以用錢衡量？」接連便是難懂的話，什麼「打晒莉法主線又同你講」，什麼「為咗直葉學劍道」之類，引得眾人都鬨笑起來：動物台內外充滿了快活的空氣。"},{"pid":"466f194aa87083f82a160de9030180c2513efc64","tid":337024,"uid":57911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T03:13:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef9369633558b0dcbfee1e0b255cf6b7fe25bbc8","tid":337024,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T03:14:39.000Z","msg":"ok"},{"pid":"7bf02065da5792d90893e6e028c2eebe60723d41","tid":337024,"uid":57911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T03:38:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"644ff9fb26e14a80feac460524123d76b78cf109","tid":337024,"uid":14719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":